This version uses a flat, contiguous representation of the matrices for better cache performance, applies blocking to keep working data sets small and tile‑aware, and parallelises the outer loops with OpenMP. The algorithmic behaviour (exact floating‑point results in IEEE 754 sense) matches the original implementation.

